item.dc:creator: @Pwnd Pwnd
item.description:
@Pwnd wrote:

[quote=“magma828, post:1, topic:217411”][quote]404 - Page not found
The page you wished to access could not be found.
(http://pwnds.info/upload/?p=aup)[/quote]

yey no aup =]
I also want an account so I can browse the images n stuff :).

It’s good in the way files are not directly downloaded (mysql?) but you should let images be directly accessed. You could also do what other hosting sites do and use a timer.[/quote]Although, there will be an AUP ;]
And don’t worry. The registration system is my highest priority for this project.
I don’t want to use a timer because all major (Gay) file hosting services piss me off with them.

[quote=“magma828, post:1, topic:217426”]Adding to what ThAt0n36Uy said, the ads shouldn’t be under the footer. That makes it look like you’re using some shitty host that sticks on advertisements to every page.[/quote]You give me another spot to put it, and I’ll do it.

[quote=“Unhandled, post:4, topic:217394”]Make a SilverLight client so you can upload with nice progress bars and whatnot.[/quote]I plan to make everything from scratch (Well, with the help of JS Prototype that is ;])
